.TH PFBTOPFA 1 "13 February 2002" 6.53 Ghostscript \" -*- nroff -*-
.SH NAME
pfbtopfa \- Convert Postscript .pfb fonts to .pfa format using ghostscript
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpfbtopfa\fR \fIinput.pfb\fR \fI[output.pfa]\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
This script invokes
.BR gs (1)
to convert a .pfb file into a .pfa file.
.SH SEE ALSO
gs(1)
.SH VERSION
This document was last revised for Ghostscript version 6.53.
